WEBVTT

00:00.602 --> 00:02.078
<i>Previously on "Bitten".</i>

00:02.086 --> 00:03.320
The Pack's rule is being challenged.

00:03.354 --> 00:04.883
They want The Pack destroyed.

00:04.900 --> 00:07.234
Right now we need to
go on the offensive.

00:07.268 --> 00:09.790
Jeremy: Turning humans into an
army of werewolves is bad enough.

00:09.833 --> 00:11.200
Recruiting serial killers...

00:11.236 --> 00:12.602
Elena: My life here with you,

00:12.637 --> 00:13.703
that's the life that I want.

00:13.738 --> 00:14.905
What about Clay?

00:14.939 --> 00:16.440
Clay: What we have between us

00:16.474 --> 00:19.243
is the real thing or
it's not, you decide.

00:19.277 --> 00:21.277
Jeremy: What were you able to
find out about James Williams?

00:21.311 --> 00:23.513
Fake website run by some
guy named Nate Parker.

00:23.548 --> 00:25.348
Just looking for the guy
that used to live here.

00:25.382 --> 00:27.651
Only person that lived here
was an old hag named Liz,

00:27.685 --> 00:28.818
and definitely no Nate.

00:28.853 --> 00:31.521
It's time to storm the castle.

00:31.556 --> 00:34.290
(Grunting)

00:34.324 --> 00:35.525
Logan!

00:35.560 --> 00:36.860
(Wolf growling)

00:36.894 --> 00:38.227
Jakob Fenn. His father's still alive,

00:38.262 --> 00:39.346
maybe he'd want these.

00:39.371 --> 00:40.448
Logan: She's gone! Rachel!

00:40.472 --> 00:41.772
I've got to find her, she can't run.

00:41.807 --> 00:44.408
- Hey, hey.
- The baby!

00:44.442 --> 00:45.810
Malcom Danvers, it's a pleasure
to finally meet you.

00:45.844 --> 00:48.045
What is it that you really want, father?

00:48.080 --> 00:49.446
A future.

00:49.481 --> 00:50.881
Her.

00:50.916 --> 00:52.116
(Heavy breathing)

00:52.150 --> 00:54.551
(Screaming)

00:56.187 --> 00:59.227
( ♪ )

01:05.727 --> 01:07.694
Man: (On speaker)
<i>Once again from the top.</i>

01:07.729 --> 01:09.496
My name is Nate Parker.

01:09.531 --> 01:11.731
I was hired by
Malcolm Danvers a year ago

01:11.765 --> 01:14.133
to run the Toronto part of his plan.

01:14.167 --> 01:17.202
The video of the wolves, I shot that.

01:20.607 --> 01:21.707
<i>Once again.</i>

01:21.742 --> 01:23.943
My name is Nate Parker!

01:23.977 --> 01:25.477
Others were part of the Stonehaven plan,

01:25.512 --> 01:27.312
Mutts that bit in psychopaths.

01:27.347 --> 01:29.448
I didn't... I didn't have
anything to do with that.

01:29.482 --> 01:30.649
<i>Once again.</i>

01:30.683 --> 01:32.751
There's a meeting.

01:32.785 --> 01:35.320
New recruits. I can tell you where.

01:35.355 --> 01:37.456
I'll tell you everything
you want to know.

01:37.490 --> 01:39.758
(Sobbing) Malcolm Danvers is
the one you want, I swear!

01:39.792 --> 01:41.893
(Click)
(Gasp)

01:41.928 --> 01:43.395
(Yelping)

01:43.430 --> 01:45.664
Wh... what was... what... what was that?

01:45.698 --> 01:46.731
What the hell was that?

01:46.766 --> 01:48.066
(Click)

01:48.100 --> 01:50.468
S...s... some... something touched me!

01:50.502 --> 01:53.438
( ♪ )

01:53.472 --> 01:55.540
It was all Malcolm's idea!

01:55.575 --> 01:57.108
He's the one you want!

01:57.142 --> 01:59.644
I've... I've told you
where his house is,

01:59.679 --> 02:01.512
where the others are meeting.

02:01.547 --> 02:03.647
He may be there, whatever
else do you want to know?

02:03.682 --> 02:05.283
I will tell you!

02:08.954 --> 02:10.721
(Gasp)

02:10.755 --> 02:12.056
Hello?

02:15.527 --> 02:17.695
Hello!

02:17.729 --> 02:20.297
(Shriek)

02:21.933 --> 02:23.333
Are you there?

02:26.638 --> 02:29.807
What... wh... wh... wh...
what did you do to me?

02:31.977 --> 02:33.276
Hello!

02:34.745 --> 02:36.279
Why aren't you talking?

