03:37.206 --> 03:38.373
Oof!

03:44.079 --> 03:46.981
(Screaming)

03:47.015 --> 03:48.349
(Grunting)

03:51.820 --> 03:54.622
(Snarling)

03:54.657 --> 03:58.500
