09:38.682 --> 09:41.250
♪ Don't mean I'm gon' pay

09:41.284 --> 09:43.953
♪ You can send me a piano

09:43.987 --> 09:45.788
♪ Don't mean I'm gon' play

09:47.825 --> 09:49.792
♪ I heard you call

09:49.827 --> 09:53.463
♪ Through a broken window

09:53.497 --> 09:59.235
♪ Saxophones in a grown man's
